These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, march, december
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in october##7
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Birthday   | march | december       | may | october        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, april, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Birthday   | january   | june | april | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
4 different pets are kept: horse, pony, goat, goldfish
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the horse##7
3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Pet   | goat | horse  | goldfish   | pony |

