.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, game, old-henry, havana
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the havana-smoker##7
3. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | game | davidoff | havana       | old-henry |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
City: colone, rome, paris, london
1. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person traveling to london is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| City   | colone      | rome | london      | paris |

