.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, electronic, dubstep, salsa
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of dubstep is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
6. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of folk and the fan of electronic##7
7. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | salsa | electronic   | dubstep |

