.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
City: rome, san-francisco, venice, hannover
1. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| City   | rome | venice | hannover    | san-francisco |

