.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, western, fantasy, documentary
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the person watching western movies is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching drama movies##7
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | fantasy | western | drama |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

