The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, r&b, techno
1. the person drinking mirinda is not the fan of classical##6
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person drinking coffee##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | mirinda | fanta | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | r&b      | classical | pop            |

