.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, dutch, british, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. the indonesian is somewhere between the pakistani and the owner of the snake##7
2. the dutch is not the owner of the rat##6
3. the owner of the mouse is not the british##6
4. the british is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the pakistani is the owner of the dog##1
6. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | indonesian | dutch | british |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

