.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-12::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, carrot, grapefruit, kale
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person eating kale##6
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the person eating apple is somewhere between the person eating kale and the person eating carrot##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Food   | carrot | apple | grapefruit | kale |
| Sport   | tennis  | sailing    | climbing    | skiing  |

