The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, march, april
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's birthday is in april##7
2. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in march##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku     | drawing     | rock-climbing |
| Birthday     | april | march | december | may     |

