.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, manager, nurse, teacher
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, reading, gardening, collecting
1. the teacher is on the right of the freelancer##1
2. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
3. the manager is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
4. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the manager##7
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the freelancer##1
7. the teacher is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Job           | manager | nurse  | freelancer  | teacher |
| Hobby   | baking  | collecting | reading | gardening   |

