2. the pilot is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the writer is somewhere to the left of the engineer##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
5. the pilot is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
6. the writer is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
