.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish, snake
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, chaman, game
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the old-henry-smoker and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Cigar   | chaman | game  | pall-mall | old-henry |

 